1. *Seronjo* je dete često plakalo. (The child was often crying sadly.)
2. Ona je kao *seronja* bežala iz sobe. (She ran away from the room sadly.)
3. Kada se seti njegovog izdajstva, žena se *seronjila*. (When she remembered his betrayal, the woman sadly sighed.)
4. Njegovo *seronjstvo* se prelilo u suze. (His sadness turned into tears.)
5. *Seronjila* je kroz ceo dan. (She was sad all day.)